Weapons and military equipment for army [Courtesy]  The East African Community has been urged to enhance women participation in weapons management.  Speaking at a Regional Centre on Small Arms (Recsa) conference in Nairobi, peace and conflict expert Dr Sellah King’oro cited a history of male dominance and stereotypes against women in security institutions.  “Recsa member states and other stakeholders should enhance the visibility of women professionals.”        By Kamau Muthoni | 8 hours ago By Kamau Muthoni | 8 hours ago By Daniel Chege | 8 hours ago By Hudson Gumbihi | 8 hours ago